{"tid":301594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"The Blue Party :【回應大專學界聲明】英國貢獻香港良多","createTime":"2017-06-28T18:28:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T04:35:59.000Z","uid":92301,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2c0175508c29f541d934044fd057a71d135cdaec","tid":301594,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T18:28:49.000Z","msg":"針對大專學界聲明，The Blue Party 認為有幾點需要修改，並肯定英方對香港的貢獻。<br />\n<br />\nEP. 2 Discuss on Declaration of Students' Union of Higher Institutions/ 回應大專學界聲明<br />\n<br />\nFilmed in Belfast/ 攝於貝城<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1201814499930719&amp;id=275143252597853\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1201814499930719%26id%3D275143252597853&d=jzoBtcDn5a4I92ZefLOOqcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=1f4861bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1201814499930719&amp;id=275143252597853</a><br />\n<br />\nThe Blue Party 相信，文化乃一地之魂、歷史乃一地之根、合二者可正視聽、締自由之本。惟今有見教育政策忽視、故吾社望盡所能以發掘本土文化、重塑歷史真相、以所集所學所識傳掦我埠。吾社雖以文史研究為本、亦涉獵社會事務、以實踐理念。<br />\n<br />\nThe Blue Party 將不定期舉辦展覽、講座及導賞團等活動、敬請留意本 page 更新。"},{"pid":"c4ac1f80a86c563e67c38ae41a23a7c301c02b80","tid":301594,"uid":82391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T19:35:52.000Z","msg":"The blue party 係民族黨d fd?"},{"pid":"d3134cb663475c0cc0ca9ce693aa1a0751369036","tid":301594,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T02:43:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>The blue party 係民族黨d fd?</blockquote><br />\n唔知，但風格有啲似香港獨立黨"},{"pid":"cf201e246231b97295f357fdfe735a162983392c","tid":301594,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T06:16:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e08fb294c2780673a944c018f85f3abb004834ee","tid":301594,"uid":82391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T06:21:20.000Z